OL,3,C'I just lay there in agony:' secret
OL,4,Cfilming reveals more NHS corridor care
OL,6,FSome NHS hospitals in England may
OL,7,F'have no choice' but to use corridors
OL,8,Fto care for patients, as ITV News
OL,9,FHealth Correspondent Rebecca Barry
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FFootage captured by ITV News shows
OL,13,Fdozens of patients being cared for in
OL,14,Fthe corridors of an NHS hospital.
OL,16,FFilmed on Wednesday at the Royal
OL,17,FLiverpool University Hospital, it
OL,18,Fshows patients and their relatives
OL,19,Fleft in the crowded corridors of the
OL,20,Fhospital's emergency department.
