OL,3,C'I just lay there in agony:' secret
OL,4,Cfilming reveals more NHS corridor care
OL,6,FHealthcare experts say treating
OL,7,Fpatients in corridors is unsafe and
OL,8,Fundignified.
OL,10,FIn April 2024, Valerie Johnstone spent
OL,11,F29 hours on a trolley in the corridor
OL,12,Fof the Royal Liverpool.
OL,14,F"I just lay there in agony," Valerie
OL,15,Ftold ITV News.
OL,17,F"My disease that I've got, all you
OL,18,Fneed is to be rehydrated and pain
OL,19,Frelief and a toilet ` and I had none
OL,20,Fof that," she said.
