OL,3,C'I just lay there in agony:' secret
OL,4,Cfilming reveals more NHS corridor care
OL,6,FValerie, who is a former nurse,
OL,7,Fexplained how she obtained pain relief
OL,8,Ffrom the overstretched nursing team.
OL,10,F"I ended up crawling off the trolley
OL,11,Fand crawled around the corner to the
OL,12,Fnurse station," Valerie said.
OL,14,F"I'll die in my bed before I go back
OL,15,Fto the hospital because I don't want
OL,16,Fto lie in a corridor in agony. I might
OL,17,Fas well lie in my bed in agony,"
OL,18,FValerie told ITV News.
