OL,4,Cfilming reveals more NHS corridor care
OL,6,FIf you or a family member has been
OL,7,Faffected by this story, you can email
OL,8,Fus at investigations@itv.com
OL,10,FA report by the Health Services Safety
OL,11,FInvestigations Body (HSSIB) on
OL,12,FThursday found that some NHS hospitals
OL,13,Fare adapting their corridors to
OL,14,Fprovide care there by installing plug
OL,15,Fsockets and emergency call bells.
OL,17,FThe HSSIB visited 13 hospitals between
OL,18,FAugust and December last year and
OL,19,Ffound that corridor care was being
OL,20,Fused regularly.
