OL,3,C'I just lay there in agony:' secret
OL,4,Cfilming reveals more NHS corridor care
OL,6,F"Shocking levels of care are becoming
OL,7,Fthe new norm. It is not right and it's
OL,8,Fnot what any of us want," Professor
OL,9,FNicola Ranger, General Secretary and
OL,10,FChief Executive of the Royal College
OL,11,Fof Nursing, told ITV News.
OL,13,F"We fully understand why hospitals are
OL,14,Ftrying to adapt their environment for
OL,15,Fpatients that they don't have clear
OL,16,Fidentified space for but it's a bit of
OL,17,Fa tragedy that that is what we're
OL,18,Fhaving to do," Professor Ranger added.
