OL,3,C'I just lay there in agony:' secret
OL,4,Cfilming reveals more NHS corridor care
OL,6,FITV News has been investigating the
OL,7,Fscale of 'corridor care' in England's
OL,8,FNHS, revealing it to be taking place
OL,9,Fin hospitals right across the country.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for NHS University
OL,12,FHospitals of Liverpool Group said:
OL,14,F"Receiving care on a corridor is not
OL,15,Fthe experience we want for any of our
OL,16,Fpatients, and our staff are working
OL,17,Fincredibly hard to provide safe and
OL,18,Fdignified care in what can be
OL,19,Fchallenging circumstances.
