OL,6,F"Over the last year we have reduced
OL,7,Fthe use of corridor care compared to
OL,8,Fprevious years.
OL,10,F"To manage increased demand on our
OL,11,Fservices during the winter period, we
OL,12,Fhave opened additional beds within our
OL,13,Fhospitals and we continue to work
OL,14,Fclosely with health and social care
OL,15,Fpartners to increase discharges into
OL,16,Fthe community."
