OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid:
OL,10,F"No-one should receive care in a
OL,11,Fcorridor ` the situation we inherited
OL,12,Fis unacceptable and undignified, and
OL,13,Fwe are determined to end it.
OL,15,F"That is why NHS England is working
OL,16,Fclosely with trusts to reduce
OL,17,Fvariation, tackle inconsistencies,
OL,18,Fimprove data collection and reduce
OL,19,Fdischarge delays, alongside social
OL,20,Fcare colleagues.
